{"tid":723201,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝同新移民親戚飲茶","createTime":"2018-06-30T07:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T09:02:15.000Z","uid":173357,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"05f7b126e7e3cc1d8ca5778412dbc50024d8fca6","tid":723201,"uid":173357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"佢地一家5口係15年前移民過黎香港，我印象中好似已經超過10年冇見面，係之前我吖爺過身既時候先見翻！今日約出黎一齊飲茶！記得佢地啱啱落黎香港果陣我仲去過佢地係大角咀租既劏房，覺得佢地好撚慘！後黎我媽仲攞我啲舊衫畀佢地！今日同佢地傾計先知佢地今日已經係香港買咗3層樓，一間地舖，除咗兩層樓仲供緊，其他都已經供滿！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來佢地係沙士期間執咗平貨！飲完茶，我同我老豆老母同吖妹冇點講嘢若有所思咁翻咗秀茂坪既公屋度！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：冚家土生土長香港人"},{"pid":"76d5cee56dd096b491340f14403cdfeff1ec2902","tid":723201,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70e1ce7ae3d9328f59feab25c6848324475e0fdb","tid":723201,"uid":44534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T08:04:09.000Z","msg":"有眼光就無計啦"},{"pid":"e853d378af2e5657a7e5122d085de01267969780","tid":723201,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T08:07:43.000Z","msg":"15年前2003年"},{"pid":"aed9d783b42a4db5120510b9dcc687a36827a9ac","tid":723201,"uid":173357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T08:32:16.000Z","msg":"間舖當年2球都唔駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111f0a1a4ca28c03e8adfa6fa8a00b2039794a1f","tid":723201,"uid":186388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T08:37:00.000Z","msg":"一落香港就識買樓？"},{"pid":"67f1c66f9bacd85c5c031df29a6e01f17cf3353d","tid":723201,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T08:38:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">15年都叫新移民？<br />\n咁識左15年嘅fd都叫陌新人啦！</span>"},{"pid":"b9c46b568833b1c6e92a7e2e5cc423954caae817","tid":723201,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0